            "b;BlackBackground",
            "s;;Default Controls:{br}'Z' key: CONFIRM{br}'X' key: CANCEL{br}'S' key: START{br}'C' key: INFO{br}'A' key: AUX;center;StyleNid=cinematic;NumLines=6",
            "s;;These controls can be reconfigured in the Options menu which is accessible by pressing START or AUX while on the map.;center;StyleNid=cinematic",
            "chapter_title;Chapter Sound",
            "end_skip",
            "m;Star Poem",
            "s;;In this land exists the <red>Fire Emblem</>,{br}an ancient artifact said to have{br}protected humanity from calamity.;;180;hint;NumLines=3",
            "s;;A great evil will threaten the land one day, and a young lord will rise up, Fire Emblem in hand, to quell it.;;180;hint;NumLines=3",
            "s;;But today is not the beginning of that story.;;140;hint;NumLines=2",
            "s;;Today, the foundations of their path are laid out to prepare them for their destiny.;;160;hint;NumLines=3",
            "s;;But first thing's first...;;140;hint;NumLines=1",
            "s;;Who is this young lord?;;140;hint;NumLines=1",
            "uu;LordMale;Left;LordFemale;Right",
            "choice;LordGender;Choose a gender:;Male,Female",
            "rrr",
            "if;v('LordGender') == 'Female'",
            "  add_tag;Lord;Female",
            "  change_portrait;Lord;LordFemale",
            "  set_variant;Lord;Female",
            "  lvar;LordPronouns;{'Personal':'she','PersonalC':'She','PersonalO':'her','PersonalOC':'Her','PosessiveS':'her','PossessiveSC':'Her','PossessiveP':'hers','PossessivePC':'Hers','Reflexive':'herself','ReflexiveC':'Herself','Noun':'woman','NounC':'Woman','Address':'milady','AddressC':'Milady','Address1C':'Lady','Address2':'princess'}",
            "else",
            "  lvar;LordPronouns;{'Personal':'he','PersonalC':'He','PersonalO':'him','PersonalOC':'Him','PosessiveS':'his','PossessiveSC':'His','PossessiveP':'his','PossessivePC':'His','Reflexive':'himself','ReflexiveC':'Himself','Noun':'man','NounC':'Man','Address':'milord','AddressC':'Milord','Address1C':'Lord','Address2':'prince'}",
            "end",
            "end_skip",
            "s;;What will the name of this young lord be?;;150;hint;NumLines=2",
            "lvar;NamePrompt;'Enter name.'",
            "trigger_script;0 Name Entry",
            "set_name;Lord;{v:LordName}",
            "s;;Yes, this is the start of {v:LordName}'s journey.;;;hint;NumLines=2",
            "s;;A long road of hardship and growth is ahead of {e:v('LordPronouns')['PersonalO']}, but {e:v('LordPronouns')['Personal']} won't be alone.;;;hint",
            "s;;You will be there to guide {e:v('LordPronouns')['PersonalO']}, after all.;;;hint;NumLines=2",
            "s;;Yes, <red>YOU</>.{w} This is what you were destined for as well, is it not?;;130;hint;NumLines=3",
            "s;;Now, please, tell me about yourself.;;100;hint;NumLines=2",
            "uu;JagenMale;Left;JagenFemale;Right",
            "choice;JagenGender;Choose your gender.;Male,Female",
            "rrr",
            "if;v('JagenGender') == 'Female'",
            "  add_tag;Player;Female",
            "  change_portrait;Player;JagenFemale",
            "  set_variant;Player;Female",
            "  add_tag;Player;Female",
            "  lvar;JagenPronouns;{'Personal':'she','PersonalC':'She','PersonalO':'her','PersonalOC':'Her','PosessiveS':'her','PossessiveSC':'Her','PossessiveP':'hers','PossessivePC':'Hers','Reflexive':'herself','ReflexiveC':'Herself','Noun':'woman','NounC':'Woman','Address1C':'Lady'}",
            "else",
            "  lvar;JagenPronouns;{'Personal':'he','PersonalC':'He','PersonalO':'him','PersonalOC':'Him','PosessiveS':'his','PossessiveSC':'His','PossessiveP':'his','PossessivePC':'His','Reflexive':'himself','ReflexiveC':'Himself','Noun':'man','NounC':'Man','Address1C':'Sir'}",
            "end",
            "end_skip",
            "s;;And your name?;;100;hint;NumLines=1",
            "text_entry;JagenName;Enter your name.;8;numbers_and_punctuation;Athol",
            "set_name;Player;{v:JagenName}",
            "end_skip",
            "s;;{v:JagenName}, hm?{br}A fine name, indeed.;;120;hint;NumLines=2",
            "s;;This journey is {v:LordName}'s{br}as well as yours, {v:JagenName}.;;100;hint",
            "s;;The both of you will grow and change as time passes.;;;hint;NumLines=3",
            "s;;You may be hardened and experienced, but that doesn't mean you haven't stopped living.;;;hint",
            "s;;You'll come to understand that soon enough.;;130;hint;NumLines=2",
            "s;;Now, enough chit-chat.{w} I'm sure you're eager to see your young ward.;;;hint;NumLines=3",
            "s;;Go on, wake up. Can't keep {e:v('LordPronouns')['PersonalO']} waiting!;;;hint;NumLines=2",
            "t;close",
            "b;Bedroom",
            "t;open",
            "end_skip",
            "u;Player;Right;;CloseEyes",
            "s;Player;*yawn*|{c:e;Player;HalfCloseEyes}That dream again{tgm}...{tgm} It feels like I've been having it more frequently lately.|{c:e;Player;CloseEyes}I hope it isn't a bad omen.",
            "e;Player;NormalBlink",
            "bop;Player",
            "s;Player;Oh, it's almost eight o' clock. I should head to the throne room.|I must make a good first impression on the {e:v('LordPronouns')['Address2']} of Chronos.",
            "r;Player",
            "t;close",
            "b;CastleBright",
            "t;open",
            "end_skip",
            "music_clear",
            "m;Morning Glory",
            "uu;Player;Right;Lord;Left",
            "e;Lord;Smile",
            "s;Lord;Greetings. You must be the new tactician.|Did you have a good night's rest?",
            "s;Player;Yes, thank you, Your Highness.|Please, allow me to properly introduce myself.|{c:e;Player;Smile}I am {v:JagenName}. It is a pleasure to meet you.",
            "s;Lord;The pleasure is all mine, {e:v('JagenPronouns')['Address1C']} {v:JagenName}. I am {v:LordName}.|I have heard great things about you from Father.|He's told me all about your exploits on the battlefield.|I am very much looking forward to working with you.",
            "s;Player;As am I, {e:v('LordPronouns')['Address']}.|{c:e;Player;HalfCloseEyes,NoSmile}Though, I must admit, all this praise has me a little self-conscious.|{c:e;Player;CloseEyes}I only hope I can live up to these expectations.",
            "s;Lord;I'm sure you will, {e:v('JagenPronouns')['Address1C']} {v:JagenName}.|You're making a good first impression already.|We of Chronos value time-earned wisdom and strength.|I'm sure my father saw these qualities in you when he first considered you for the position.|{c:e;Lord;NoSmile}Speaking of which, you know of your duties for this upcoming year, correct?",
            "e;Player;NormalBlink",
            "s;Player;To familiarize myself with the kingdom and its culture,|and to train you, {e:v('LordPronouns')['AddressC']}, in military strategy and tactics.",
            "e;Lord;Smile",
            "s;Lord;Good to see that you are on top of things, {e:v('JagenPronouns')['Address1C']} {v:JagenName}.|I'm sure this will be the beginning of a prosperous partnership.|Now, shall we head out?|This would be the perfect time to begin our training together.",
            "s;Player;As you wish, {e:v('LordPronouns')['Address']}.",
            "rrr",
            "t;close",
            "b",
            "t;open",
            "end_skip",
            "uu;Player;Right;Lord;Left",
            "s;Lord;My father gave us some money to get us started for the month.|Your regular monthly salary of 1000G will be in effect starting in April.",
            "e;Player;Smile",
            "s;Player;Excellent. Please give him my thanks.",
            "give_money;5000",
            "s;Lord;Now, {e:v('JagenPronouns')['Address1C']} {v:JagenName}, as a newcomer to the kingdom,|I believe it would be wise to familiarize yourself with the castle town.|Take the time to visit the local businesses and speak with the townsfolk.|They will all be quite helpful for this year of training together.|{c:e;Player;Smile}As should be expected of the kingdom's future ruler,|I am already familiar with the area. I shall lead the way.",
            "e;Player;NoSmile",
            "s;Player;Yes, Your Highness.",
            "e;Lord;NoSmile",
            "s;Lord;And if you need to review anything the townspeople tell you,|go back to the castle and <red>Check Guide</>.|The castle provides other useful information, so <red>it may be wise to check things there first</>.|If you would like a suggestion for another destination,|I recommend visiting the <red>watchtower</>.",
            "rrr",
            "center_cursor;enemywatch",
            "flicker_cursor;enemywatch",
            "center_cursor;Lord",
            "uu;Player;Right;Lord;Left",
            "s;Lord;The soldiers there are not only dutiful but also quite knowledgeable.|{c:e;Lord;Smile}They'll also talk your ear off given the opportunity.",
            "s;Player;Haha, I see. I'll keep that in mind, Your Highness.",
            "rrr",
